        "timestamp": "2019-05-21 14:45:32.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis is simply moving the VES specs from VNFSDK to VNR Requirements as discussed.  I did the minimal amount of editing to ensure all RST errors and warnings were resolved.  I will create a separate review to remove the contents from VNFSDK.  \n\nIf you have more substantial feedback on the content itself, please open a JIRA ticket and we will address that in the El Alto release.\n\nNote: there were a number of orphan documents and artifacts that were VES related in VNFSDK, but do not seem to be referenced by any documents.  I did not bring those over.  I am going to check and see what the VES authors want to do with those.  I will not delete that content from VNFSDK until I have a clear direction on what to do with them.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
